{"tid":438684,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[[ Whatsapp 山Group ]] 廢hike","createTime":"2017-10-17T07:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T02:00:47.000Z","uid":44550,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d9aadc433c0bd1e44ddd288a65341dec623c8fe0","tid":438684,"uid":44550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T07:07:54.000Z","msg":"尋找一眾行山愛好者，不論男女老幼，不論新手老手亦都歡迎，歡迎大家在群組內開團行山，本人希望製作一個平台比大家交流行山和分享行山的樂趣，所以盡可能不干預大家。<br />\n<ins>本群並沒有任何特別規矩</ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">先小人後君子</span></span></strong><br />\n本群定期清人, 謝絕潛水員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果收到大量人士投訴某人行為不檢，某人將會被踢離開本群(事前會徵詢其他組員意見)<br />\n<br />\n本群活動純屬私人自願參加，一切意外及責任與領導和籌劃人員無關。請留意自身安全，報名前必先了解路線，如有不適請盡早揚聲 <br />\n如果有興趣請填少少資料, 我地會盡快加你入Group. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1qK-BeezeoC6Xqjm8sBd9aJCZ66MBPn0hrCDYTasIFTU/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1qK-BeezeoC6Xqjm8sBd9aJCZ66MBPn0hrCDYTasIFTU%2Fedit&d=qlbzF595bKFOyyzyv%2BzMXQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=eb77b485\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1qK-BeezeoC6Xqjm8sBd9aJCZ66MBPn0hrCDYTasIFTU/edit</a>"},{"pid":"3b8aa5cb93c4c63d6838593373c74ddae13a9b8b","tid":438684,"uid":44550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T07:28:36.000Z","msg":"夜獅團<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/152642_39c936602419736cb728915992c0abe8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F152642_39c936602419736cb728915992c0abe8.jpg&h=69d6e74c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/152829_4810374ef9347c5f23371b0b9f60f018.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F152829_4810374ef9347c5f23371b